token_info.name: HICVERSE [14/03/2021]
token_info.description: Interactive 3D Graph Visualization of the hic et nunc's users [blue spheres], OBJKTs [multi-colored spheres] and their connections (ownership[blue lines]/collection[white lines]). HIC's Main Minter was excluded from this visualization to make it less cluttered. In other words, only OBJKTs that were collected at least once appear in this graph. Format: GLTF. Size: ~12MB. Data collected: 14/03/2021. See in Dark Mode for best experience :) Made by @sandromiccoli
